//hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Travis-Perkins-Logo-AI.png\" alt=\"Travis-Perkins-Logo-AI\" width=\"91\" height=\"94\" />            <img class=\"wp-image-435 alignnone\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/wates-logo.png\" alt=\"wates-logo\" width=\"140\" height=\"78\" />          <img class=\" size-full wp-image-556 alignnone\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Wickes.png\" alt=\"Wickes\" width=\"165\" height=\"110\" /></p>','Some Companies We Work With','','publish','open','open','','companies-we-work-with','','','2015-06-15 11:15:22','2015-06-15 10:15:22','',7,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?page_id=416',0,'page','',0),(45,1,'2015-03-10 13:41:46','2015-03-10 13:41:46','<h1>A STATEMENT THAT SAYS SOMETHING ABOUT HIPPO BEING A NATIONAL WASTE COLLECTION SERVICE</h1>','Home','','inherit','open','open','','17-revision-v1','','','2015-03-10 13:41:46','2015-03-10 13:41:46','',17,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=45',0,'revision','',0),(46,1,'2015-03-10 14:03:55','2015-03-10 14:03:55','','Business Solutions <i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i>','','publish','open','open','','46','','','2015-05-20 07:11:08','2015-05-20 06:11:08','',0,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=46',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(47,1,'2015-03-10 14:03:55','2015-03-10 14:03:55','','Read our Case Studies <i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i>','','publish','open','open','','read-our-case-studies','','','2015-05-20 07:11:08','2015-05-20 06:11:08','',0,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=47',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(48,1,'2015-03-10 14:03:55','2015-03-10 14:03:55','','About Us <i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i>','','publish','open','open','','48','','','2015-05-20 07:11:08','2015-05-20 06:11:08','',0,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=48',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(50,1,'2015-03-10 14:59:18','2015-03-10 14:59:18',' ','','','publish','open','open','','50','','','2015-03-10 15:00:59','2015-03-10 15:00:59','',6,'http://hippo.tailor