ring a domestic remodelling. HIPPOBAGs ensure that waste is kept neatly and takes up as little room as possible.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGs come flat packed, so don’t waste room before they are used. In addition, our reliable and flexible courier service means that you can arrange for your HIPPOBAG to be picked up at a convenient time for you. HIPPOBAGS can also be left on your – or your customer’s – property, making them far more tidy and convenient than a traditional skip that would be left on the road.\r\n\r\nFor bathroom installations, the 1.5 cubic yard MEGABAG is ideal, able to hold an entire bathroom suite. The larger 4.5 Yard HIPPOSKIP was developed to accommodate kitchen and larger bathroom installation projects.','Services','','inherit','open','open','','6-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 10:04:05','2015-03-11 10:04:05','',6,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=77',0,'revision','',0),(76,2,'2015-03-11 10:02:27','2015-03-11 10:02:27','Choosing a waste logistics company is a vital decision. Not only do you need a service that’s professional, affordable and environmentally responsible; you require a solution that takes care of everything from collection to disposal, so you’re free to focus on your project.\r\n\r\nWhen you choose HIPPOWASTE you know you will benefit from:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>a nationwide network for rapid collection</li>\r\n	<li>competitive pricing and market leading service</li>\r\n	<li>over 90% of your waste being recycled</li>\r\n	<li>valuable time and space saved on site, as you only use the space you need</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAt HIPPO, we provide a bespoke and reliable waste solutions that help you reduce costs, save time, and meet your responsibilities.\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Construction Waste</span></strong>\r\n\r\nThe construction industry is the single largest producer of waste in the UK, generating some 120 million tonnes of waste annually. We understand that a variety of waste can be produced in construction tasks, an