act, so you can use us for unexpected waste events whenever you need us. With thousands of HIPPOBAGS collected from store estates weekly, HIPPO provides a flexible, convenient and ethical service for your business.\r\n<h2>Housing and Renovation</h2>\r\nWe have collected over half a million HIPPOBAGs from residential properties, so we understand the challenges of waste disposal in the process of improving social housing and transforming neighbourhoods.\r\n<h2>Retail and Office Fitout</h2>\r\nDuring the refurbishment or fit out stage of retail and office premises, using a HIPPOBAG allows you to segregate waste streams on site, helping you to achieve increased recycling rates. This in return helps you to achieve your diversion from landfill objectives.\r\n\r\nWith HIPPOWASTE you’ll also benefit from the flexibility of an instant and non-bulky waste solution that is transportable and bespoke to your project. HIPPOWASTE work around your business, with our flat packed bags able to be used at any time – up to a year –after purchase, and being collected at a time of your convenience. This way you no-longer have to wait for skip deliveries or collections that clutter sites, hampering the progress of your workforce.\r\n<h2>Plasterboard Recycling</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE also offer a quick and cost effective way of getting rid of plasterboard from your site or property. Through our dedicated plasterboard disposal and recycling scheme, we recycle 100% of uncontaminated plasterboard that we collect. HIPPO’s environmental values mean that you can ensure that you are disposing of your waste in a responsible and eco-friendly manner.\r\n<h2>Installations</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE offers an ideal service for installations. We understand the importance of minimising disruption and inconvenience to customers and their surrounding properties during a domestic remodelling. HIPPOBAGs ensure that waste is kept neatly and takes up as little room as possible.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGs come flat packed, so don’t waste room before they are used. In addition, our reliable and flexible courier service means that you can arrange for your HIPPOBAG to be picked up at a convenient time for you. HIPPOBAGS can also be left on your – or your customer’s – property, making them far more tidy and convenient than a traditional skip that would be left on the road.\r\n\r\nFor bathroom installations, the 1.5 cubic yard MEGABAG is ideal, able to hold an entire bathroom suite. The larger 4.5 Yard HIPPOSKIP was developed to accommodate kitchen and larger bathroom installation projects.','Services','','inherit','open','open','','6-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 10:10:27','2015-03-11 10:10:27','',6,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=82',0,'revision','',0),(84,2,'2015-03-11 10:12:27','2015-03-11 10:12:27','','facilities-management-icon','','inherit','open','open','','facilities-management-icon','','','2015-03-11 10:12:34','2015-03-11 10:12:34','',6,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities-management-icon.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(282,2,'2015-03-13 12:14:40','2015-03-13 12:14:40','HIPPO offer an effective service for use during the refurbishment or fit-out stage of retail and office premises.\r\n\r\nUsing a HIPPOBAG allows you to segregate waste streams on site, making it easy for you to increase your recycling rates, in turn helping you to achieve your diversion from landfill objectives.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGs are a waste logistics solution without the space or time restrictions that you will encounter when either buying a skip or handling waste logistics yourself. With the efficiencies in time and space that are delivered by HIPPOWASTE, your workforce will be more productive and your business will save money.\r\n\r\nHIPPO offer an affordable, flexible and instant waste solution that is both transportable and bespoke to your project. In addition, HIPPOBAGs allow you to carry out the work at a suitable time for you, rather than when you are able to hire a skip. This way you can take greater control of your waste logistics operation and avoid unnecessary hassle during your retail or office fit out project.\r\n\r\nHIPPO’s strong, non-bulky skip alternatives come in three different sizes, so you can match the size of the HIPPOBAG you purchase to the size of the project you are undertaking, meaning that you will never pay for more than you need and will save valuable space around your project.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/case-studies/retail-case-study/\">Read our retail and office fit-out case study here</a>.','Retail and Office Fit-out','','inherit','open','open','','13-revision-v1','','','2015-03-13 12:14:40','2015-03-13 12:14:40','',13,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(251,2,'2015-03-12 10:54:31','2015-03-12 10:54:31','HIPPO offer an effective service for use during the refurbishment or fit-out stage of retail and office premises.\r\n\r\nUsing a HIPPOBAG allows you to segregate waste streams on site, making it easy for you to increase your recycling rates, in turn helping you to achieve your diversion from landfill objectives.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGs are a waste logistics solution without the space or time restrictions that you will encounter when either buying a skip or handling waste logistics yourself. With the efficiencies in time and space that are delivered by HIPPOWASTE, your workforce will be more productive and your business will save money.\r\n\r\nHIPPO offer an affordable, flexible and instant waste solution that is both transportable and bespoke to your project. In addition, HIPPOBAGs allow you to carry out the work at a suitable time for you, rather than when you are able to hire a skip. This way you can take greater control of your waste logistics operation and avoid unnecessary hassle during your retail or office fit out project.\r\n\r\nHIPPO’s strong, non-bulky skip alternatives come in three different sizes, so you can match the size of the HIPPOBAG you purchase to the size of the project you are undertaking, meaning that you will never pay for more than you need and will save valuable space around your project.\r\n\r\nRead our retail and office fit-out case study <a title=\"Case Study: Interior Fit-Out\" href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/case-studies/case-study-two/\">here</a>.','Retail and Office Fit-out','','inherit','open','open','','13-revision-v1','','','2015-03-12 10:54:31','2015-03-12 10:54:31','',13,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(87,1,'2015-03-11 10:19:48','2015-03-11 10:19:48','<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">HIPPO provides a National Waste Logistics service; offering an ethical, cost-effective and convenient alternative to skip hire</h1>','Home','','inherit','open','open','','17-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 10:19:48','2015-03-11 10:19:48','',17,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=87',0,'revision','',0),(88,2,'2015-03-11 10:19:55','2015-03-11 10:19:55','HIPPO™ is a national provider of innovative and integrated waste logistics solutions, the HIPPOWASTE service caters to the needs of building and construction professionals for their waste removal.\r\n\r\nDriven by the desire to provide an affordable, convenient and reliable waste logistics service for your business, HIPPOWASTE use our innovative yellow HIPPOBAG. These large, strong and convenient skip alternatives are bought flat-packed from either our website of from our trusted retailers, and can be used at a time of your convenience. Once your HIPPOBAG is full, our expert couriers will take it off your hands and dispose of it responsibly.\r\n\r\nHIPPO take our environmental responsibilities very seriously, recycling 90% of the waste that we collect. In addition, our strong reputation for delivering high standards of customer care in a niche area of the waste logistics market has meant we have experienced significant growth in just seven years of trading.\r\n\r\n<h2>Here to Clear</h2>\r\n\r\nFor smaller waste logistics needs, HIPPOWASTE’s Here to Clear van is ideal. This service is especially suited to areas where access is restricted to waste and where it needs to be manually cleared.\r\n\r\nThese vans carry two of our HIPPO employees, who will ensure that your waste logistics process is carried out seamlessly.  We use a Ford Transit Tipper wan for this service, which is able to hold up to 14 yards or a ton of waste. Using this service incurs an additional charge.\r\n\r\n<h2>HIPPOPRO</h2>\r\n\r\nHIPPOPRO is our service for professional tradesmen, providing the essential tool for your trade. We are trusted by tradesmen around the UK to deliver excellent, affordable and simple service to dispose of your excess waste.\r\n\r\nYou can save space and money by choosing the right sized HIPPOBAG for your business needs, from the 1 yard MIDIBAG, to the 1.5 yard MEGABAG and 4.5 yard HIPPOSKIP. Avoid cluttering up your customers’ driveways with unsightly skips and instead place neat, professional looking HIPPOBAGS at a convenient place for you.\r\n\r\nAs a tradesman you can also enjoy a saving of at least 5% on waste disposal every time that you make a collection with HIPPOPRO.\r\n\r\n<h2>Careers at HIPPO</h2>\r\n\r\nWe at HIPPO are always looking for new members of our team. If you think you have the skills required to become part of our thriving business, then we may well have a space for you at HIPPO.','About','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 10:19:55','2015-03-11 10:19:55','',8,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=88',0,'revision','',0),(89,2,'2015-03-11 10:21:21','2015-03-11 10:21:21','HIPPO™ is a national provider of innovative and integrated waste logistics solutions, the HIPPOWASTE service caters to the needs of building and construction professionals for their waste removal.\r\n\r\nDriven by the desire to provide an affordable, convenient and reliable waste logistics service for your business, HIPPOWASTE use our innovative yellow HIPPOBAG. These large, strong and convenient skip alternatives are bought flat-packed from either our website of from our trusted retailers, and can be used at a time of your convenience. Once your HIPPOBAG is full, our expert couriers will take it off your hands and dispose of it responsibly.\r\n\r\nHIPPO take our environmental responsibilities very seriously, recycling 90% of the waste that we collect. In addition, our strong reputation for delivering high standards of customer care in a niche area of the waste logistics market has meant we have experienced significant growth in just seven years of trading.\r\n\r\n<h2>Here to Clear</h2>\r\n\r\nFor smaller waste logistics needs, HIPPO’s Here to Clear van is ideal. This service is especially suited to areas where access is restricted to waste and where it needs to be manually cleared.\r\n\r\nThese vans carry two of our HIPPO employees, who will ensure that your waste logistics process is carried out seamlessly.  We use a Ford Transit Tipper van for this service, which is able to hold up to 14 yards or a ton of waste. Using this service incurs an additional charge.\r\n\r\n<h2>HIPPOPRO</h2>\r\n\r\nHIPPOPRO is our service for professional tradesmen, providing the essential tool for your trade. We are trusted by tradesmen around the UK to deliver excellent, affordable and simple service to dispose of your excess waste.\r\n\r\nYou can save space and money by choosing the right sized HIPPOBAG for your business needs, from the 1 yard MIDIBAG, to the 1.5 yard MEGABAG and 4.5 yard HIPPOSKIP. Avoid cluttering up your customers’ driveways with unsightly skips and instead place neat, professional looking HIPPOBAGS at a convenient place for you.\r\n\r\nAs a tradesman you can also enjoy a saving of at least 5% on waste disposal every time that you make a collection with HIPPOPRO.\r\n\r\n<h2>Careers at HIPPO</h2>\r\n\r\nWe at HIPPO are always looking for new members of our team. If you think you have the skills required to become part of our thriving business, then we may well have a space for you at HIPPO.','About','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 10:21:21','2015-03-11 10:21:21','',8,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=89',0,'revision','',0),(116,2,'2015-03-11 11:28:35','2015-03-11 11:28:35','<h1><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction-icon1.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-94\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction-icon1-150x150.png\" alt=\"construction-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Construction</h1>','Construction','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 11:28:35','2015-03-11 11:28:35','',10,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=116',0,'revision','',0),(117,2,'2015-03-11 11:29:02','2015-03-11 11:29:02','<h1><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction-icon1.png\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-94\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction-icon1-150x150.png\" alt=\"construction-icon\" width=\"90\" height=\"90\" /></a>Construction</h1>','Construction','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 11:29:02','2015-03-11 11:29:02','',10,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=117',0,'revision','',0),(530,2,'2015-06-01 11:20:29','2015-06-01 10:20:29','Ensuring that existing housing supply across the country is well-maintained and meets a minimum standard of decency is fundamental to healthy and happy communities. HIPPO is ideally placed to support refurbishment projects in this vital field.\r\n\r\nWe have a thorough grasp of the challenges in disposing of waste generated in the process of creating and improving affordable housing and transforming neighbourhoods – compounded by operating to strict deadlines and within tight budgets.\r\n<h2>hassle free collection</h2>\r\nHIPPO has collected over 500,000 bags from domestic properties since 2005. With this level of experience you can be sure of a safe and hassle free collection from your customer’s property. We can also help you to maintain your reputation as a good corporate citizen and fulfil your duty of care to the communities in which you work, by minimising the social and environmental impact of your operations.\r\n<h2>Nationwide</h2>\r\nHIPPO provide a nationwide network for rapid collection, meaning that you can use our services for your waste logistics needs wherever you are in the country.\r\n<h2>3 bag sizes</h2>\r\nWe offer a choice of 3 bag sizes, meaning that whatever size project you\'re undertaking, we have the perfect bag for you to complete your job. These bags come flat packed, so there is no need to wait for a skip or have to worry about regional skip prices and availability.\r\n\r\nAs well as reducing the direct costs of waste management, we can improve operational efficiencies and minimise disruption and distractions to your core activities. A typical sized homes project produces 2-5 cubic yards of waste from kitchen units, bathroom suites, and central heating systems. HIPPOBAGs, from the 1 cubic yard MIDIBAG to the 4.5 yard MIGHTYBAG, are ideal for the disposal of these waste streams. MEGABAGs were designed to hold a bathroom suite and a single MIGHTYBAG has the capacity to hold both a bathroom suite and a medium kitchen.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-383\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction1.jpg\" alt=\"construction HIPPO\" width=\"1200\" height=\"578\" /></a>','Housing and Renovation','','inherit','open','open','','11-revision-v1','','','2015-06-01 11:20:29','2015-06-01 10:20:29','',11,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/11-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(111,2,'2015-03-11 10:46:35','2015-03-11 10:46:35','<h1>Careers</h1>\r\n\r\nThe chances are, when you join us, you’ve got more than a job in mind. You’ll be thinking about how joining HIPPO will contribute to your longer term aims – and so will we.\r\nWe work to provide opportunities for development through both training and through career development. Our training is themed around individuals’ career objectives, departmental requirements, and wider business needs or changes, making sure we’re all ready for our next challenge.\r\nWe are particularly proud of our team’s career progression – we’re not a huge organisation, but through creative thinking, an eye for talent, and the flexibility that comes with the Company’s growth and development, we have been able to spot opportunities for people to move to roles which are more senior, more challenging, or represent a change of career. This is great for us, as we retain our committed and talented people; and it allows people with talent and ambition to pursue their career aspirations. 9% of our team were promoted into their current roles, and 12% have moved to a different role during their time with HIPPO.\r\n\r\nTo apply for any of vacancies, please email your CV with a covering letter to recruitment@hippowaste.co.uk or post it to: HR Department, HIPPO, 1000 Lakeside, North Harbour, Portsmouth PO6 3EN\r\n\r\n<h2> Current Vacancies </h2>\r\nWe have no current vacancies.','Careers at HIPPOWASTE','','inherit','open','open','','34-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 10:46:35','2015-03-11 10:46:35','',34,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=111',0,'revision','',0),(91,2,'2015-03-11 10:23:01','2015-03-11 10:23:01','<h2>Why Choose HIPPO? </h2>\r\nSelecting a waste logistics service is a vital decision for any business. HIPPOWASTE provide a reliable, affordable and convenient national skip alternative for any sized business. Our innovative HIPPOBAG comes in three convenient sizes and is available either online or from our trusted stockists around the UK.\r\n\r\nA HIPPOBAG is the perfect alternative to traditional skip hire for a number of reasons; a HIPPOBAG is bought flat packed and can be used at a convenient time for you, where you would have a limited time if you hired a skip. When you are finished with your HIPPOBAG, simply arrange a collection and our professional couriers will collect your waste and dispose of it responsibly.\r\nHIPPOBAGs also take up very little space and you can suit the size of bag to the size of your project, this means you don’t need to pay the full price that you would for a skip if your needs are smaller.\r\n\r\nHIPPO’s environmental policies mean that you can be reassured that your waste is being handled and disposed of in a responsible manner. We typically recycle around 90% of the waste that we collect. HIPPO are also committed to excellent customer service and have an excellent average customer review rating of 4.7 out of 5.\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Waste Logistics Experts</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE provide waste logistics services for a great number of projects. Whether you require waste management in projects such as as new build and construction, housing and renovation, facilities management, kitchen and bathroom installation, retail and office fit out or virtually any project where waste is produced. HIPPOWASTE also run a dedicated plasterboard disposal and recycling scheme, where we collect uncontaminated plasterboard and recycle 100% of it.\r\n\r\nWith HIPPO’s trusted, project–specific approach we can suit our service perfectly to your waste logistics needs, whilst ensuring that you receive value for money and that your waste is dealt with responsibly.','About Us','','inherit','open','open','','33-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 10:23:01','2015-03-11 10:23:01','',33,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=91',0,'revision','',0),(93,2,'2015-03-11 10:27:17','2015-03-11 10:27:17','<h2>Contact Us</h2>\r\nIf you have any questions or queries about HIPPOWASTE, we’d love to hear from you! \r\n\r\nYou can get in touch with us via email or phone:\r\nBook Collection: 0345 850 0 850\r\n(Lines Open 08:00 until 18:00 Monday – Friday excluding Bank Holidays)\r\nEmail: sales@hippowaste.co.uk\r\n\r\nIf you are a domestic or DIY customer and are looking for information relating to local stockists or buying your HIPPOBAGS™ online then please visit our newly developed retail website – hippobag.co.uk.\r\n\r\nLet us work with you to design the waste solution that fits your needs and saves you time and money. Enter your contact information below and one of our dedicated Account Managers will call to discuss your project.\r\n\r\nHead Office:  HIPPO™, 1000 Lakeside, North Harbour, Portsmouth, Hampshire, PO6 3EN','Contact Us','','inherit','open','open','','35-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 10:27:17','2015-03-11 10:27:17','',35,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=93',0,'revision','',0),(94,2,'2015-03-11 10:31:12','2015-03-11 10:31:12','','construction-icon','','inherit','open','open','','construction-icon-2','','','2015-03-11 10:31:24','2015-03-11 10:31:24','',6,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction-icon1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(95,2,'2015-03-11 10:31:14','2015-03-11 10:31:14','','facilities-management-icon','','inherit','open','open','','facilities-management-icon-2','','','2015-03-11 10:32:51','2015-03-11 10:32:51','',6,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities-management-icon1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(96,2,'2015-03-11 10:31:15','2015-03-11 10:31:15','','housing-rennovation-icon','','inherit','open','open','','housing-rennovation-icon','','','2015-03-11 10:33:02','2015-03-11 10:33:02','',6,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/housing-rennovation-icon.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(97,2,'2015-03-11 10:31:16','2015-03-11 10:31:16','','installation-icon','','inherit','open','open','','installation-icon','','','2015-03-11 10:33:40','2015-03-11 10:33:40','',6,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/installation-icon.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(98,2,'2015-03-11 10:31:17','2015-03-11 10:31:17','','plasterboard-icon','','inherit','open','open','','plasterboard-icon','','','2015-03-11 10:33:24','2015-03-11 10:33:24','',6,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/plasterboard-icon.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(99,2,'2015-03-11 10:31:18','2015-03-11 10:31:18','','retail-offices-fitout-icon','','inherit','open','open','','retail-offices-fitout-icon','','','2015-03-11 10:33:11','2015-03-11 10:33:11','',6,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-offices-fitout-icon.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(100,2,'2015-03-11 10:31:49','2015-03-11 10:31:49','Choosing a waste logistics company is a vital decision. Not only do you need a service that’s professional, affordable and environmentally responsible; you require a solution that takes care of everything from collection to disposal, so you’re free to focus on your project.\r\n\r\nWhen you choose HIPPOWASTE you know you will benefit from:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>a nationwide network for rapid collection</li>\r\n	<li>competitive pricing and market leading service</li>\r\n	<li>over 90% of your waste being recycled</li>\r\n	<li>valuable time and space saved on site, as you only use the space you need</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAt HIPPO, we provide a bespoke and reliable waste solutions that help you reduce costs, save time, and meet your responsibilities.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction-icon1.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-94\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction-icon1-150x150.png\" alt=\"construction-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Construction Waste</h2>\r\nThe construction industry is the single largest producer of waste in the UK, generating some 120 million tonnes of waste annually. We understand that a variety of waste can be produced in construction tasks, and ensure that even hazardous waste and plasterboard are dealt with responsibly and efficiently in our waste logistics projects.\r\n\r\nWith HIPPO, you only have to deal with one supplier for all of your waste disposal needs, meaning that we can develop a bespoke solution for your specific needs – giving you maximum efficiency and flexibility even in the largest of construction waste logistics tasks.\r\n<h2>Facilities Management</h2>\r\nUsing the HIPPOBAG to deal with heavy or bulk inert waste streams and ad hoc waste events will provide you with a number of benefits in managing waste disposal across your national or regional store estate. By working together with any existing waste contracts you have, we can assist you in reconstructing your waste services.\r\n\r\nOur service is not a regular scheduled waste collection covered by a bin contract, so you can use us for unexpected waste events whenever you need us. With thousands of HIPPOBAGS collected from store estates weekly, HIPPO provides a flexible, convenient and ethical service for your business.\r\n<h2>Housing and Renovation</h2>\r\nWe have collected over half a million HIPPOBAGs from residential properties, so we understand the challenges of waste disposal in the process of improving social housing and transforming neighbourhoods.\r\n<h2>Retail and Office Fitout</h2>\r\nDuring the refurbishment or fit out stage of retail and office premises, using a HIPPOBAG allows you to segregate waste streams on site, helping you to achieve increased recycling rates. This in return helps you to achieve your diversion from landfill objectives.\r\n\r\nWith HIPPOWASTE you’ll also benefit from the flexibility of an instant and non-bulky waste solution that is transportable and bespoke to your project. HIPPOWASTE work around your business, with our flat packed bags able to be used at any time – up to a year –after purchase, and being collected at a time of your convenience. This way you no-longer have to wait for skip deliveries or collections that clutter sites, hampering the progress of your workforce.\r\n<h2>Plasterboard Recycling</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE also offer a quick and cost effective way of getting rid of plasterboard from your site or property. Through our dedicated plasterboard disposal and recycling scheme, we recycle 100% of uncontaminated plasterboard that we collect. HIPPO’s environmental values mean that you can ensure that you are disposing of your waste in a responsible and eco-friendly manner.\r\n<h2>Installations</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE offers an ideal service for installations. We understand the importance of minimising disruption and inconvenience to customers and their surrounding properties during a domestic remodelling. HIPPOBAGs ensure that waste is kept neatly and takes up as little room as possible.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGs come flat packed, so don’t waste room before they are used. In addition, our reliable and flexible courier service means that you can arrange for your HIPPOBAG to be picked up at a convenient time for you. HIPPOBAGS can also be left on your – or your customer’s – property, making them far more tidy and convenient than a traditional skip that would be left on the road.\r\n\r\nFor bathroom installations, the 1.5 cubic yard MEGABAG is ideal, able to hold an entire bathroom suite. The larger 4.5 Yard HIPPOSKIP was developed to accommodate kitchen and larger bathroom installation projects.','Services','','inherit','open','open','','6-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 10:31:49','2015-03-11 10:31:49','',6,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=100',0,'revision','',0),(101,2,'2015-03-11 10:33:44','2015-03-11 10:33:44','Choosing a waste logistics company is a vital decision. Not only do you need a service that’s professional, affordable and environmentally responsible; you require a solution that takes care of everything from collection to disposal, so you’re free to focus on your project.\r\n\r\nWhen you choose HIPPOWASTE you know you will benefit from:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>a nationwide network for rapid collection</li>\r\n	<li>competitive pricing and market leading service</li>\r\n	<li>over 90% of your waste being recycled</li>\r\n	<li>valuable time and space saved on site, as you only use the space you need</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAt HIPPO, we provide a bespoke and reliable waste solutions that help you reduce costs, save time, and meet your responsibilities.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction-icon1.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-94\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction-icon1-150x150.png\" alt=\"construction-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Construction Waste</h2>\r\nThe construction industry is the single largest producer of waste in the UK, generating some 120 million tonnes of waste annually. We understand that a variety of waste can be produced in construction tasks, and ensure that even hazardous waste and plasterboard are dealt with responsibly and efficiently in our waste logistics projects.\r\n\r\nWith HIPPO, you only have to deal with one supplier for all of your waste disposal needs, meaning that we can develop a bespoke solution for your specific needs – giving you maximum efficiency and flexibility even in the largest of construction waste logistics tasks.\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities-management-icon1.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-95\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities-management-icon1-150x150.png\" alt=\"facilities-management-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Facilities Management</h2>\r\nUsing the HIPPOBAG to deal with heavy or bulk inert waste streams and ad hoc waste events will provide you with a number of benefits in managing waste disposal across your national or regional store estate. By working together with any existing waste contracts you have, we can assist you in reconstructing your waste services.\r\n\r\nOur service is not a regular scheduled waste collection covered by a bin contract, so you can use us for unexpected waste events whenever you need us. With thousands of HIPPOBAGS collected from store estates weekly, HIPPO provides a flexible, convenient and ethical service for your business.\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/housing-rennovation-icon.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-96\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/housing-rennovation-icon-150x150.png\" alt=\"housing-rennovation-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Housing and Renovation</h2>\r\nWe have collected over half a million HIPPOBAGs from residential properties, so we understand the challenges of waste disposal in the process of improving social housing and transforming neighbourhoods.\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-offices-fitout-icon.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-99\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-offices-fitout-icon-150x150.png\" alt=\"retail-offices-fitout-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Retail and Office Fitout</h2>\r\nDuring the refurbishment or fit out stage of retail and office premises, using a HIPPOBAG allows you to segregate waste streams on site, helping you to achieve increased recycling rates. This in return helps you to achieve your diversion from landfill objectives.\r\n\r\nWith HIPPOWASTE you’ll also benefit from the flexibility of an instant and non-bulky waste solution that is transportable and bespoke to your project. HIPPOWASTE work around your business, with our flat packed bags able to be used at any time – up to a year –after purchase, and being collected at a time of your convenience. This way you no-longer have to wait for skip deliveries or collections that clutter sites, hampering the progress of your workforce.\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-98\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/plasterboard-icon-150x150.png\" alt=\"plasterboard-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />Plasterboard Recycling</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE also offer a quick and cost effective way of getting rid of plasterboard from your site or property. Through our dedicated plasterboard disposal and recycling scheme, we recycle 100% of uncontaminated plasterboard that we collect. HIPPO’s environmental values mean that you can ensure that you are disposing of your waste in a responsible and eco-friendly manner.\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/installation-icon.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-97\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/installation-icon-150x150.png\" alt=\"installation-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Installations</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE offers an ideal service for installations. We understand the importance of minimising disruption and inconvenience to customers and their surrounding properties during a domestic remodelling. HIPPOBAGs ensure that waste is kept neatly and takes up as little room as possible.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGs come flat packed, so don’t waste room before they are used. In addition, our reliable and flexible courier service means that you can arrange for your HIPPOBAG to be picked up at a convenient time for you. HIPPOBAGS can also be left on your – or your customer’s – property, making them far more tidy and convenient than a traditional skip that would be left on the road.\r\n\r\nFor bathroom installations, the 1.5 cubic yard MEGABAG is ideal, able to hold an entire bathroom suite. The larger 4.5 Yard HIPPOSKIP was developed to accommodate kitchen and larger bathroom installation projects.','Services','','inherit','open','open','','6-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 10:33:44','2015-03-11 10:33:44','',6,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=101',0,'revision','',0),(107,2,'2015-03-11 10:41:15','2015-03-11 10:41:15','<h1>Services</h1>\r\nChoosing a waste logistics company is a vital decision. Not only do you need a service that’s professional, affordable and environmentally responsible; you require a solution that takes care of everything from collection to disposal, so you’re free to focus on your project.\r\n\r\nWhen you choose HIPPOWASTE you know you will benefit from:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>a nationwide network for rapid collection</li>\r\n	<li>competitive pricing and market leading service</li>\r\n	<li>over 90% of your waste being recycled</li>\r\n	<li>valuable time and space saved on site, as you only use the space you need</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAt HIPPO, we provide a bespoke and reliable waste solutions that help you reduce costs, save time, and meet your responsibilities.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction-icon1.png\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-94\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction-icon1-150x150.png\" alt=\"construction-icon\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\" /></a> Construction Waste</h2>\r\nThe construction industry is the single largest producer of waste in the UK, generating some 120 million tonnes of waste annually. We understand that a variety of waste can be produced in construction tasks, and ensure that even hazardous waste and plasterboard are dealt with responsibly and efficiently in our waste logistics projects.\r\n\r\nWith HIPPO, you only have to deal with one supplier for all of your waste disposal needs, meaning that we can develop a bespoke solution for your specific needs – giving you maximum efficiency and flexibility even in the largest of construction waste logistics tasks.\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities-management-icon1.png\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-95\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities-management-icon1-150x150.png\" alt=\"facilities-management-icon\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\" /></a> Facilities Management</h2>\r\nUsing the HIPPOBAG to deal with heavy or bulk inert waste streams and ad hoc waste events will provide you with a number of benefits in managing waste disposal across your national or regional store estate. By working together with any existing waste contracts you have, we can assist you in reconstructing your waste services.\r\n\r\nOur service is not a regular scheduled waste collection covered by a bin contract, so you can use us for unexpected waste events whenever you need us. With thousands of HIPPOBAGS collected from store estates weekly, HIPPO provides a flexible, convenient and ethical service for your business.\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/housing-rennovation-icon.png\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/housing-rennovation-icon-150x150.png\" alt=\"housing-rennovation-icon\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\" /></a> Housing and Renovation</h2>\r\nWe have collected over half a million HIPPOBAGs from residential properties, so we understand the challenges of waste disposal in the process of improving social housing and transforming neighbourhoods.\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-offices-fitout-icon.png\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-99\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-offices-fitout-icon-150x150.png\" alt=\"retail-offices-fitout-icon\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\" /></a> Retail and Office Fitout</h2>\r\nDuring the refurbishment or fit out stage of retail and office premises, using a HIPPOBAG allows you to segregate waste streams on site, helping you to achieve increased recycling rates. This in return helps you to achieve your diversion from landfill objectives.\r\n\r\nWith HIPPOWASTE you’ll also benefit from the flexibility of an instant and non-bulky waste solution that is transportable and bespoke to your project. HIPPOWASTE work around your business, with our flat packed bags able to be used at any time – up to a year –after purchase, and being collected at a time of your convenience. This way you no-longer have to wait for skip deliveries or collections that clutter sites, hampering the progress of your workforce.\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-98\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/plasterboard-icon-150x150.png\" alt=\"plasterboard-icon\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\" /> Plasterboard Recycling</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE also offer a quick and cost effective way of getting rid of plasterboard from your site or property. Through our dedicated plasterboard disposal and recycling scheme, we recycle 100% of uncontaminated plasterboard that we collect. HIPPO’s environmental values mean that you can ensure that you are disposing of your waste in a responsible and eco-friendly manner.\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/installation-icon.png\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-97\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/installation-icon-150x150.png\" alt=\"installation-icon\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\" /></a> Installations</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE offers an ideal service for installations. We understand the importance of minimising disruption and inconvenience to customers and their surrounding properties during a domestic remodelling. HIPPOBAGs ensure that waste is kept neatly and takes up as little room as possible.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGs come flat packed, so don’t waste room before they are used. In addition, our reliable and flexible courier service means that you can arrange for your HIPPOBAG to be picked up at a convenient time for you. HIPPOBAGS can also be left on your – or your customer’s – property, making them far more tidy and convenient than a traditional skip that would be left on the road.\r\n\r\nFor bathroom installations, the 1.5 cubic yard MEGABAG is ideal, able to hold an entire bathroom suite. The larger 4.5 Yard HIPPOSKIP was developed to accommodate kitchen and larger bathroom installation projects.','Services','','inherit','open','open','','6-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 10:41:15','2015-03-11 10:41:15','',6,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=107',0,'revision','',0),(102,2,'2015-03-11 10:34:35','2015-03-11 10:34:35','Choosing a waste logistics company is a vital decision. Not only do you need a service that’s professional, affordable and environmentally responsible; you require a solution that takes care of everything from collection to disposal, so you’re free to focus on your project.\r\n\r\nWhen you choose HIPPOWASTE you know you will benefit from:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>a nationwide network for rapid collection</li>\r\n	<li>competitive pricing and market leading service</li>\r\n	<li>over 90% of your waste being recycled</li>\r\n	<li>valuable time and space saved on site, as you only use the space you need</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAt HIPPO, we provide a bespoke and reliable waste solutions that help you reduce costs, save time, and meet your responsibilities.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction-icon1.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-94\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction-icon1-150x150.png\" alt=\"construction-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a> Construction Waste</h2>\r\nThe construction industry is the single largest producer of waste in the UK, generating some 120 million tonnes of waste annually. We understand that a variety of waste can be produced in construction tasks, and ensure that even hazardous waste and plasterboard are dealt with responsibly and efficiently in our waste logistics projects.\r\n\r\nWith HIPPO, you only have to deal with one supplier for all of your waste disposal needs, meaning that we can develop a bespoke solution for your specific needs – giving you maximum efficiency and flexibility even in the largest of construction waste logistics tasks.\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities-management-icon1.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-95\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities-management-icon1-150x150.png\" alt=\"facilities-management-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a> Facilities Management</h2>\r\nUsing the HIPPOBAG to deal with heavy or bulk inert waste streams and ad hoc waste events will provide you with a number of benefits in managing waste disposal across your national or regional store estate. By working together with any existing waste contracts you have, we can assist you in reconstructing your waste services.\r\n\r\nOur service is not a regular scheduled waste collection covered by a bin contract, so you can use us for unexpected waste events whenever you need us. With thousands of HIPPOBAGS collected from store estates weekly, HIPPO provides a flexible, convenient and ethical service for your business.\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/housing-rennovation-icon.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-96\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/housing-rennovation-icon-150x150.png\" alt=\"housing-rennovation-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a> Housing and Renovation</h2>\r\nWe have collected over half a million HIPPOBAGs from residential properties, so we understand the challenges of waste disposal in the process of improving social housing and transforming neighbourhoods.\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-offices-fitout-icon.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-99\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-offices-fitout-icon-150x150.png\" alt=\"retail-offices-fitout-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a> Retail and Office Fitout</h2>\r\nDuring the refurbishment or fit out stage of retail and office premises, using a HIPPOBAG allows you to segregate waste streams on site, helping you to achieve increased recycling rates. This in return helps you to achieve your diversion from landfill objectives.\r\n\r\nWith HIPPOWASTE you’ll also benefit from the flexibility of an instant and non-bulky waste solution that is transportable and bespoke to your project. HIPPOWASTE work around your business, with our flat packed bags able to be used at any time – up to a year –after purchase, and being collected at a time of your convenience. This way you no-longer have to wait for skip deliveries or collections that clutter sites, hampering the progress of your workforce.\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-98\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/plasterboard-icon-150x150.png\" alt=\"plasterboard-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /> Plasterboard Recycling</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE also offer a quick and cost effective way of getting rid of plasterboard from your site or property. Through our dedicated plasterboard disposal and recycling scheme, we recycle 100% of uncontaminated plasterboard that we collect. HIPPO’s environmental values mean that you can ensure that you are disposing of your waste in a responsible and eco-friendly manner.\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/installation-icon.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-97\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/installation-icon-150x150.png\" alt=\"installation-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a> Installations</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE offers an ideal service for installations. We understand the importance of minimising disruption and inconvenience to customers and their surrounding properties during a domestic remodelling. HIPPOBAGs ensure that waste is kept neatly and takes up as little room as possible.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGs come flat packed, so don’t waste room before they are used. In addition, our reliable and flexible courier service means that you can arrange for your HIPPOBAG to be picked up at a convenient time for you. HIPPOBAGS can also be left on your – or your customer’s – property, making them far more tidy and convenient than a traditional skip that would be left on the road.\r\n\r\nFor bathroom installations, the 1.5 cubic yard MEGABAG is ideal, able to hold an entire bathroom suite. The larger 4.5 Yard HIPPOSKIP was developed to accommodate kitchen and larger bathroom installation projects.','Services','','inherit','open','open','','6-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 10:34:35','2015-03-11 10:34:35','',6,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=102',0,'revision','',0),(104,2,'2015-03-11 10:37:30','2015-03-11 10:37:30','<h1>Services </h1>\r\n\r\nChoosing a waste logistics company is a vital decision. Not only do you need a service that’s professional, affordable and environmentally responsible; you require a solution that takes care of everything from collection to disposal, so you’re free to focus on your project.\r\n\r\nWhen you choose HIPPOWASTE you know you will benefit from:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>a nationwide network for rapid collection</li>\r\n	<li>competitive pricing and market leading service</li>\r\n	<li>over 90% of your waste being recycled</li>\r\n	<li>valuable time and space saved on site, as you only use the space you need</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAt HIPPO, we provide a bespoke and reliable waste solutions that help you reduce costs, save time, and meet your responsibilities.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction-icon1.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-94\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction-icon1-150x150.png\" alt=\"construction-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a> Construction Waste</h2>\r\nThe construction industry is the single largest producer of waste in the UK, generating some 120 million tonnes of waste annually. We understand that a variety of waste can be produced in construction tasks, and ensure that even hazardous waste and plasterboard are dealt with responsibly and efficiently in our waste logistics projects.\r\n\r\nWith HIPPO, you only have to deal with one supplier for all of your waste disposal needs, meaning that we can develop a bespoke solution for your specific needs – giving you maximum efficiency and flexibility even in the largest of construction waste logistics tasks.\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities-management-icon1.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-95\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities-management-icon1-150x150.png\" alt=\"facilities-management-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a> Facilities Management</h2>\r\nUsing the HIPPOBAG to deal with heavy or bulk inert waste streams and ad hoc waste events will provide you with a number of benefits in managing waste disposal across your national or regional store estate. By working together with any existing waste contracts you have, we can assist you in reconstructing your waste services.\r\n\r\nOur service is not a regular scheduled waste collection covered by a bin contract, so you can use us for unexpected waste events whenever you need us. With thousands of HIPPOBAGS collected from store estates weekly, HIPPO provides a flexible, convenient and ethical service for your business.\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/housing-rennovation-icon.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-96\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/housing-rennovation-icon-150x150.png\" alt=\"housing-rennovation-icon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a> Housing and Renovation</h2>\r\nWe have collected over half a million HIPPOBAGs from residential properties, so we understand the challenges of waste disposal in t