:50','2015-03-13 17:52:50','','installations','','inherit','open','open','','installations','','','2015-03-13 17:52:54','2015-03-13 17:52:54','',12,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/installations.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(355,2,'2015-03-14 09:41:05','2015-03-14 09:41:05','The MIGHTYBAG (aka the HIPPOSKIP) was designed with kitchen and large bathroom installations in mind. The 4.5 cubic yard bag is ideal for light, bulky waste, and can easily accommodate the waste created by a standard kitchen installation. In fact, our customers find that 78% of all kitchen installations fit into a single MIGHTYBAG. For bathroom installations, the 1.5 cubic yard MEGABAG will contain a complete bathroom suite, making it the perfect solution for getting rid of waste in one simple operation.\r\n\r\n<h2>flat packed</h2>\r\n\r\nAll HIPPOBAGs come flat packed, so can easily be stored until needed. In addition, the flexible sides of our bags mean that no void space is created, saving valuable room around your project. The use of a MIGHTYBAG means you pay for an average of 4.77 yds of waste per job, compared with 5.5 – 6 yards in a rigid skip. By using HIPPOWASTE you will be able to save money as well time, benefiting from the most convenient waste solution on the market.\r\n<h2>flexible</h2>\r\nWith HIPPO\'s flexible courier service, there is no need to wait for the arrival or collection of skips, meaning that you can just get on with the job and arrange a collection at a convenient time for you.\r\n\r\n<h2>savings</h2>\r\n\r\nOur customers often save as much as <strong>£70 on each rip-out</strong>. It might not sound a lot – but if you were to do 5,000 installations a year paying the industry standard cost of £175 to dispose of your waste, that would be <strong>a saving of £350,000, or 40%!</strong> At 15,000 installations a year, then that saving rises to <strong>saving of £1,050,000.</strong>','Installation','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision-v1','','','2015-03-14 09:41:05','2015-03-14 09:41:05','',12,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/12-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(327,2,'2015-03-13 17:52:58','2015-03-13 17:52:58','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-326\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/installations.jpg\" alt=\"Installations\" width=\"1000\" height=\"346\" />\r\n\r\nThe MIGHTYBAG (aka the HIPPOSKIP) was designed with kitchen and large bathroom installations in mind. The 4.5 cubic yard bag is ideal for light, bulky waste, and can easily accommodate the waste created by a standard kitchen installation. In fact, our customers find that 78% of all kitchen installations fit into a single MIGHTYBAG. For bathroom installations, the 1.5 cubic yard MEGABAG will contain a complete bathroom suite, making it the perfect solution for getting rid of waste in one simple operation.\r\n\r\nAll HIPPOBAGs come flat packed, so can easily be stored until needed. In addition, the flexible sides of our bags mean that no void space is created, saving valuable room around your project. The use of a MIGHTYBAG means you pay for an average of 4.77 yds of waste per job, compared with 5.5 – 6 yards in a rigid skip. By using HIPPOWASTE you will be able to save money as well time, benefiting from the most convenient waste solution on the market.\r\n\r\nWith HIPPO\'s flexible courier service, there is no need to wait for the arrival or collection of skips, meaning that you can just get on with the job and arrange a collection at a convenient time for you.\r\n\r\nOur customers often save as much as <strong>£70 on each rip-out</strong>. It might not sound a lot – but if you were to do 5,000 installations a year paying the industry standard cost of £175 to dispose of your waste, that would be <strong>a saving of £350,000, or 40%!</strong> At 15,000 installations a year, then that saving rises to <strong>saving of £1,050,000.</strong>','Installation','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision-v1','','','2015-03-13 17:52:58','2015-03-13 17:52:58','',12,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/12-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(329,2,'2015-03-13 17:55:58','2015-03-13 17:55:58','','plasterboard-recycling','','inherit','open','open','','plasterboard-recycling-2','','','2015-03-13 17:56:10','2015-03-13 17:56:10','',15,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/plasterboard-recycling.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(330,2,'2015-03-13 17:56:34','2015-03-13 17:56:34','<img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-329\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/plasterboard-recycling.jpg\" alt=\"Plasterboard Recyling\" width=\"500\" height=\"535\" />HIPPOWASTE can provide quick and reliable service to allow you to remove excess plasterboard from your site. As part of our commitment to responsible and ethical waste logistics, our dedicated plasterboard disposal and recycling scheme means that we recycle 100% of uncontaminated plasterboard that we collect.\r\n\r\nIn addition to collecting plasterboard, HIPPO\'s reliable, flexible and convenient service allows the segregation of different types of waste from your project. This means that you can easily increase your company’s recycling rates, as well as saving money on landfill tax.\r\n\r\nHIPPO recycle around 90 per cent of the waste that we collect, so provide a responsible method of removing waste from your project. We also offer reviews of environmental performance on a site by site basis – including a collection method, a breakdown by waste stream and percentage of landfill diversion.\r\n\r\nWe offer a national waste logistics service, meaning that both regional and national operations are ideally suited to HIPPO. We can handle your entire waste logistics operation, so there is no need for you to deal with several separate companies for your waste needs.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGS are non-bulky and lightweight, meaning that space can be saved on-site whilst you are undertaking your project. In addition to being an affordable price, strong, convenient HIPPOBAGs come in three different sizes, so you can suit the size of HIPPOBAG used for your specific project and save money.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/case-studies/plasterboard-recycling-case-study/\">Read our Plasterboard Recycling case study here.</a>','Plasterboard Recycling','','inherit','open','open','','15-revision-v1','','','2015-03-13 17:56:34','2015-03-13 17:56:34','',15,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/15-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(331,2,'2015-03-13 18:14:54','2015-03-13 18:14:54','Read our case studies about the effectiveness of HIPPOWASTE, and learn how we could help your business:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-94\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction-icon1-150x150.png\" alt=\"construction-icon\" width=\"75\" height=\"75\" />Construction</h2>\r\nWates Retails used the HIPPOWASTE service for the <a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/case-studies/construction-case-study/\">construction of Liverpool\'s John Lewis store</a>, with huge success.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-99\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-offices-fitout-icon-150x150.png\" alt=\"retail-offices-fitout-icon\" width=\"75\" height=\"75\" />Office &amp; Retail Fit-Out</h2>\r\nThe HIPPOWASTE service assisted in the <a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/case-studies/retail-case-study/\">Fit-Out of John Lewis alongside McLaren Construction</a>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-98\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/plasterboard-icon-150x150.png\" alt=\"plasterboard-icon\" width=\"75\" height=\"75\" />Plasterboard</h2>\r\nGalliford Try had some <a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/case-studies/plasterboard-recycling-case-study/\">tricky plasterboard removal which they needed HIPPO\'s help with</a>.','Case Studies','','inherit','open','open','','7-revision-v1','','','2015-03-13 18:14:54','2015-03-13 18:14:54','',7,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/7-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(334,2,'2015-03-13 18:45:12','2015-03-13 18:45:12','<h2>HIPPO provide waste logistics services to projects across the construction sector, including social housing, retail and internal fit-out.</h2>\r\n\r\nFrom helping you plan the volume and types of waste you’ll encounter, to knowing where your waste is going and what level of recycling you can achieve, HIPPO works with you from start to finish to help to deliver your project efficiently. What’s more, our national transport infrastructure means wherever you are, you will receive a reliable collection service that you can trust.\r\n\r\n<h2> Flexibility </h2>\r\n\r\nThe flexibility of HIPPOBAGs allow for easy waste collection from tight, restricted sites. In addition, our national service means we can offer you a solution wherever you are in the country.\r\n\r\nConstruction sites nationwide use HIPPO because of the convenience and reliability of our lightweight and flexible HIPPOBAGs, as well as our excellent customer service. Collections can be made from different areas on large sites, including from scaffolding or loading bays, helping you to improve site efficiency.\r\n\r\nHIPPO can also ensure that you only have one supplier for all of your site waste needs, including hazardous waste and <a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/services/plasterboard-recycling/\">plasterboard</a>. We recycle around 90 per cent of the waste that we collect, so you can rest assured that your operation will be carried out ethically and responsibly.\r\n\r\nDifferent bag sizes make it easy to segregate waste streams and achieve diversion from landfill objectives, whilst a variety of size options mean that you only ever pay for what you need, as well as saving space on site. HIPPO offer bespoke solutions developed for each site, giving you flexibility in collection volumes, as well as in the time or date of collection.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/case-studies/construction-case-study/\">Read our Construction case study here</a>.','Construction','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2015-03-13 18:45:12','2015-03-13 18:45:12','',10,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(335,2,'2015-03-13 18:45:25','2015-03-13 18:45:25','<h2>HIPPO provide waste logistics services to projects across the construction sector, including social housing, retail and internal fit-out.</h2>\r\n\r\nFrom helping you plan the volume and types of waste you’ll encounter, to knowing where your waste is going and what level of recycling you can achieve, HIPPO works with you from start to finish to help to deliver your project efficiently. What’s more, our national transport infrastructure means wherever you are, you will receive a reliable collection service that you can trust.\r\n\r\n<h2>Flexibility</h2>\r\n\r\nThe flexibility of HIPPOBAGs allow for easy waste collection from tight, restricted sites. In addition, our national service means we can offer you a solution wherever you are in the country.\r\n\r\nConstruction sites nationwide use HIPPO because of the convenience and reliability of our lightweight and flexible HIPPOBAGs, as well as our excellent customer service. Collections can be made from different areas on large sites, including from scaffolding or loading bays, helping you to improve site efficiency.\r\n\r\nHIPPO can also ensure that you only have one supplier for all of your site waste needs, including hazardous waste and <a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/services/plasterboard-recycling/\">plasterboard</a>. We recycle around 90 per cent of the waste that we collect, so you can rest assured that your operation will be carried out ethically and responsibly.\r\n\r\nDifferent bag sizes make it easy to segregate waste streams and achieve diversion from landfill objectives, whilst a variety of size options mean that you only ever pay for what you need, as well as saving space on site. HIPPO offer bespoke solutions developed for each site, giving you flexibility in collection volumes, as well as in the time or date of collection.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/case-studies/construction-case-study/\">Read our Construction case study here</a>.','Construction','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2015-03-13 18:45:25','2015-03-13 18:45:25','',10,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(340,2,'2015-03-13 19:04:30','2015-03-13 19:04:30','','construction-hippowaste','','inherit','open','open','','construction-2','','','2015-03-13 19:04:54','2015-03-13 19:04:54','',10,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(338,2,'2015-03-13 18:58:35','2015-03-13 18:58:35','','about-hippowaste','','inherit','open','open','','about-hippowaste-2','','','2015-03-13 18:58:54','2015-03-13 18:58:54','',33,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/about-hippowaste1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(403,2,'2015-03-16 11:36:56','2015-03-16 11:36:56','<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/about-hippowaste1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-338\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/about-hippowaste1.jpg\" alt=\"About HIPPOWASTE\" width=\"369\" height=\"550\" /></a>Why Choose HIPPO?</h2>\r\nSelecting a waste logistics service is a vital decision for any business. HIPPOWASTE provide a reliable, affordable and convenient national skip alternative for any sized business. Our innovative HIPPOBAG comes in three convenient sizes and is available either online or from our trusted stockists around the UK.\r\n\r\nA HIPPOBAG is the perfect alternative to traditional skip hire for a number of reasons; a HIPPOBAG is bought flat packed and can be used at a convenient time for you, where you would have a limited time if you hired a skip. When you are finished with your HIPPOBAG, simply arrange a collection and our professional couriers will collect your waste and dispose of it responsibly.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGs also take up very little space, and you can suit the size of bag to the specific needs of your project; this means you don’t need to pay the full price that you would for a skip if your needs are smaller. You can also segregate waste into different streams using HIPPOBAGs, allowing you to increase recycling rates.\r\n\r\nHIPPO’s environmental policies mean you can rest assured that your waste is being handled and disposed of in a responsible manner. We typically recycle around 90% of the waste that we collect. HIPPO are also committed to excellent customer service and have an average customer review rating of 4.7 out of 5.\r\n<h2>Our Waste Logistics Experts</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE provide waste logistics services for a huge variety of projects. Whether you require waste logistics in new build and construction, housing and renovation, facilities management, kitchen and bathroom installation, retail and office fit out or virtually any waste-producing project; HIPPO offer the ideal service for your needs.\r\n\r\nHIPPOWASTE also run a dedicated plasterboard disposal and recycling scheme, where we collect uncontaminated plasterboard and recycle 100% of it.\r\n\r\nWith HIPPO’s trusted, flexible and project–specific approach, we can suit our services perfectly to your waste logistics needs, whilst ensuring that you receive value for money and  that your waste is dealt with responsibly.','About HIPPOWASTE','','inherit','open','open','','33-revision-v1','','','2015-03-16 11:36:56','2015-03-16 11:36:56','',33,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/33-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(337,2,'2015-03-13 18:56:25','2015-03-13 18:56:25','<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/about-hippowaste1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-336 size-full\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/about-hippowaste1.jpg\" alt=\"About HIPPOWASTE\" width=\"510\" height=\"760\" /></a>Why Choose HIPPO?</h2>\r\nSelecting a waste logistics service is a vital decision for any business. HIPPOWASTE provide a reliable, affordable and convenient national skip alternative for any sized business. Our innovative HIPPOBAG comes in three convenient sizes and is available either online or from our trusted stockists around the UK.\r\n\r\nA HIPPOBAG is the perfect alternative to traditional skip hire for a number of reasons; a HIPPOBAG is bought flat packed and can be used at a convenient time for you, where you would have a limited time if you hired a skip. When you are finished with your HIPPOBAG, simply arrange a collection and our professional couriers will collect your waste and dispose of it responsibly.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGs also take up very little space, and you can suit the size of bag to the specific needs of your project; this means you don’t need to pay the full price that you would for a skip if your needs are smaller. You can also segregate waste into different streams using HIPPOBAGs, allowing you to increase recycling rates.\r\n\r\nHIPPO’s environmental policies mean you can rest assured that your waste is being handled and disposed of in a responsible manner. We typically recycle around 90% of the waste that we collect. HIPPO are also committed to excellent customer service and have an average customer review rating of 4.7 out of 5.\r\n<h2>Our Waste Logistics Experts</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE provide waste logistics services for a huge variety of projects. Whether you require waste logistics in new build and construction, housing and renovation, facilities management, kitchen and bathroom installation, retail and office fit out or virtually any waste-producing project; HIPPO offer the ideal service for your needs.\r\n\r\nHIPPOWASTE also run a dedicated plasterboard disposal and recycling scheme, where we collect uncontaminated plasterboard and recycle 100% of it.\r\n\r\nWith HIPPO’s trusted, flexible and project–specific approach, we can suit our services perfectly to your waste logistics needs, whilst ensuring that you receive value for money and  that your waste is dealt with responsibly.','About HIPPOWASTE','','inherit','open','open','','33-revision-v1','','','2015-03-13 18:56:25','2015-03-13 18:56:25','',33,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/33-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(339,2,'2015-03-13 18:59:00','2015-03-13 18:59:00','<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/about-hippowaste1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-338 size-full\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/about-hippowaste1.jpg\" alt=\"About HIPPOWASTE\" width=\"510\" height=\"760\" /></a>Why Choose HIPPO?</h2>\r\nSelecting a waste logistics service is a vital decision for any business. HIPPOWASTE provide a reliable, affordable and convenient national skip alternative for any sized business. Our innovative HIPPOBAG comes in three convenient sizes and is available either online or from our trusted stockists around the UK.\r\n\r\nA HIPPOBAG is the perfect alternative to traditional skip hire for a number of reasons; a HIPPOBAG is bought flat packed and can be used at a convenient time for you, where you would have a limited time if you hired a skip. When you are finished with your HIPPOBAG, simply arrange a collection and our professional couriers will collect your waste and dispose of it responsibly.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGs also take up very little space, and you can suit the size of bag to the specific needs of your project; this means you don’t need to pay the full price that you would for a skip if your needs are smaller. You can also segregate waste into different streams using HIPPOBAGs, allowing you to increase recycling rates.\r\n\r\nHIPPO’s environmental policies mean you can rest assured that your waste is being handled and disposed of in a responsible manner. We typically recycle around 90% of the waste that we collect. HIPPO are also committed to excellent customer service and have an average customer review rating of 4.7 out of 5.\r\n<h2>Our Waste Logistics Experts</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE provide waste logistics services for a huge variety of projects. Whether you require waste logistics in new build and construction, housing and renovation, facilities management, kitchen and bathroom installation, retail and office fit out or virtually any waste-producing project; HIPPO offer the ideal service for your needs.\r\n\r\nHIPPOWASTE also run a dedicated plasterboard disposal and recycling scheme, where we collect uncontaminated plasterboard and recycle 100% of it.\r\n\r\nWith HIPPO’s trusted, flexible and project–specific approach, we can suit our services perfectly to your waste logistics needs, whilst ensuring that you receive value for money and  that your waste is dealt with responsibly.','About HIPPOWASTE','','inherit','open','open','','33-revision-v1','','','2015-03-13 18:59:00','2015-03-13 18:59:00','',33,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/33-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(511,2,'2015-05-20 11:18:44','2015-05-20 10:18:44','<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/about-hippowaste1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-338\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/about-hippowaste1.jpg\" alt=\"About HIPPOWASTE\" width=\"369\" height=\"550\" /></a>Why Choose HIPPO?</h2>\r\nSelecting a waste logistics service is a vital decision for any business. HIPPOWASTE provide a reliable, affordable and convenient national skip alternative for any sized business. Our innovative HIPPOBAG comes in three convenient sizes and is available either online or from our trusted stockists around the UK.\r\n\r\nA HIPPOBAG is the perfect alternative to traditional skip hire for a number of reasons; a HIPPOBAG is bought flat packed and can be used at a convenient time for you, where you would have a limited time if you hired a skip. When you are finished with your HIPPOBAG, simply arrange a collection and our professional couriers will collect your waste and dispose of it responsibly.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGs also take up very little space, and you can suit the size of bag to the specific needs of your project; this means you don’t need to pay the full price that you would for a skip if your needs are smaller. You can also segregate waste into different streams using HIPPOBAGs, allowing you to increase recycling rates.\r\n\r\nHIPPO’s environmental policies mean you can rest assured that your waste is being handled and disposed of in a responsible manner. We typically recycle around 90% of the waste that we collect. HIPPO are also committed to excellent customer service and have an average customer review rating of 4.7 out of 5.\r\n<h2>Our Waste Logistics Experts</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE provide waste logistics services for a huge variety of projects. Whether you require waste logistics in new build and construction, housing and renovation, facilities management, kitchen and bathroom installation, retail and office fit out or virtually any waste-producing project; HIPPO offer the ideal service for your needs.\r\n\r\nHIPPOWASTE also run a dedicated plasterboard disposal and recycling scheme, where we collect uncontaminated plasterboard and recycle 100% of it.\r\n\r\nWith HIPPO’s trusted, flexible and project–specific approach, we can suit our services perfectly to your waste logistics needs, whilst ensuring that you receive value for money and  that your waste is dealt with responsibly.','Our Services','','inherit','open','open','','33-revision-v1','','','2015-05-20 11:18:44','2015-05-20 10:18:44','',33,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/33-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(342,2,'2015-03-13 19:05:56','2015-03-13 19:05:56','<h2>HIPPO provide waste logistics services to projects across the construction sector, including social housing, retail and internal fit-out.</h2>\r\nFrom helping you plan the volume and types of waste you’ll encounter, to knowing where your waste is going and what level of recycling you can achieve, HIPPO works with you from start to finish to help to deliver your project efficiently. What’s more, our national transport infrastructure means wherever you are, you will receive a reliable collection service that you can trust.\r\n<h2>Flexibility</h2>\r\nThe flexibility of HIPPOBAGs allow for easy waste collection from tight, restricted sites. In addition, our national service means we can offer you a solution wherever you are in the country.\r\n\r\nConstruction sites nationwide use HIPPO because of the convenience and reliability of our lightweight and flexible HIPPOBAGs, as well as our excellent customer service. Collections can be made from different areas on large sites, including from scaffolding or loading bays, helping you to improve site efficiency.\r\n\r\nHIPPO can also ensure that you only have one supplier for all of your site waste needs, including hazardous waste and <a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/services/plasterboard-recycling/\">plasterboard</a>. We recycle around 90 per cent of the waste that we collect, so you can rest assured that your operation will be carried out ethically and responsibly.\r\n\r\nDifferent bag sizes make it easy to segregate waste streams and achieve diversion from landfill objectives, whilst a variety of size options mean that you only ever pay for what you need, as well as saving space on site. HIPPO offer bespoke solutions developed for each site, giving you flexibility in collection volumes, as well as in the time or date of collection.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/case-studies/construction-case-study/\">Read our Construction case study here</a>.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction.jpg\"><img class=\"ali