hat would be <strong>a saving of £350,000, or 40%!</strong> At 15,000 installations a year, then that saving rises to <strong>saving of £1,050,000.</strong>','Installation','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision-v1','','','2015-04-08 09:40:39','2015-04-08 08:40:39','',12,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/12-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(389,2,'2015-03-16 10:59:31','2015-03-16 10:59:31','','retail-office-fitout','','inherit','open','open','','retail-office-fitout','','','2015-03-16 11:00:09','2015-03-16 11:00:09','',13,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-office-fitout.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(464,2,'2015-04-07 14:38:37','2015-04-07 13:38:37','<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-casestudy-e1426505179570.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-398\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-casestudy-e1426505179570.jpg\" alt=\"facilities HIPPO\" width=\"544\" height=\"810\" /></a>HIPPO Provide Waste Logistics Services to Retail and Office Fit-out Projects</h2>\nHIPPO offer an effective service for use during the refurbishment or fit-out stage of retail and office premises.\n\nUsing a HIPPOBAG allows you to segregate waste streams on site, making it easy for you to increase your recycling rates, in turn helping you to achieve your diversion from landfill objectives.\n<h2>Efficient</h2>\nHIPPOBAGs are a waste logistics solution without the space or time restrictions that you will encounter when either buying a skip or handling waste logistics yourself. With the efficiencies in time and space that are delivered by HIPPOWASTE, your workforce will be more productive and your business will save money.\n<h2>flexible</h2>\nHIPPO offer an affordable, flexible and instant waste solution that is both transportable and bespoke to your project. In addition, HIPPOBAGs allow you to carry out the work at a suitable time for you, rather than when you are able to hire a skip. This way you can take greater control of your waste logistics operation and avoid unnecessary hassle during your retail or office fit out project.\n<h2>3 different sizes</h2>\nHIPPO’s strong, non-bulky skip alternatives come in three different sizes, so you can match the size of the HIPPOBAG you purchase to the size of the project you are undertaking, meaning that you will never pay for more than you need and will save valuable space around your project.\n\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/case-studies/retail-case-study/\">Read our retail and office fit-out case study here</a>.\n\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-office-fitout.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-389\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-office-fitout.jpg\" alt=\"retail and office fitout HIPPO\" width=\"1200\" height=\"558\" /></a>','Retail and Office Fit-out','','inherit','open','open','','13-autosave-v1','','','2015-04-07 14:38:37','2015-04-07 13:38:37','',13,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/13-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(390,2,'2015-03-16 11:00:29','2015-03-16 11:00:29','<h2>HIPPO Provide Waste Logistics Services to Retail and Office Fit-out Projects</h2>\r\nHIPPO offer an effective service for use during the refurbishment or fit-out stage of retail and office premises.\r\n\r\nUsing a HIPPOBAG allows you to segregate waste streams on site, making it easy for you to increase your recycling rates, in turn helping you to achieve your diversion from landfill objectives.\r\n<h2>Efficient</h2>\r\nHIPPOBAGs are a waste logistics solution without the space or time restrictions that you will encounter when either buying a skip or handling waste logistics yourself. With the efficiencies in time and space that are delivered by HIPPOWASTE, your workforce will be more productive and your business will save money.\r\n<h2>flexible</h2>\r\nHIPPO offer an affordable, flexible and instant waste solution that is both transportable and bespoke to your project. In addition, HIPPOBAGs allow you to carry out the work at a suitable time for you, rather than when you are able to hire a skip. This way you can take greater control of your waste logistics operation and avoid unnecessary hassle during your retail or office fit out project.\r\n<h2>3 different sizes</h2>\r\nHIPPO’s strong, non-bulky skip alternatives come in three different sizes, so you can match the size of the HIPPOBAG you purchase to the size of the project you are undertaking, meaning that you will never pay for more than you need and will save valuable space around your project.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/case-studies/retail-case-study/\">Read our retail and office fit-out case study here</a>.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-office-fitout.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-389\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-office-fitout.jpg\" alt=\"retail and office fitout HIPPO\" width=\"1200\" height=\"558\" /></a>','Retail and Office Fit-out','','inherit','open','open','','13-revision-v1','','','2015-03-16 11:00:29','2015-03-16 11:00:29','',13,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(391,2,'2015-03-16 11:04:10','2015-03-16 11:04:10','','facilities-management','','inherit','open','open','','facilities-management-3','','','2015-03-16 11:04:24','2015-03-16 11:04:24','',14,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities-management1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(475,2,'2015-04-08 09:47:50','2015-04-08 08:47:50','<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-476\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities.jpg\" alt=\"facilities HIPPO\" width=\"687\" height=\"1020\" /></a>HIPPO Provide Waste Logistics for Facilities Management</h2>\nUsing the HIPPOBAG for the segregation of heavy or substantial inert waste streams, or for any unscheduled or ad hoc waste removal needs will benefit your business in a number of ways.\n\nHIPPO offer a professional, reliable and fully national service, meaning that we can manage your waste logistics needs across your entire regional or national store estate. HIPPOWASTE can work alongside any existing contracts that your business has in place, delivering an efficient reconstructed waste logistics operation, should you require more than your current contracts are able to deliver.\n<h2>flexible</h2>\nHIPPOWASTE offer a flexible and convenient service that can work around your needs; there are no restricting time limits when using our services and you can arrange a pick up at a suitable time for you.\n<h2>reputation</h2>\nOur reputation for facilities management services has meant that thousands of HIPPOBAGs are collected from store estates weekly. We ensure that waste we collect is disposed of in an ethical manner, with over 90 per cent of the waste that we collect being recycled.\n<h2>3 different sizes</h2>\nHIPPOBAGs come in three separate sizes and are non-bulky and affordable. Buying the right sized bag for your waste logistics needs will mean that your business will save money, as well as valuable space on site. When used throughout a business on a national or regional store level, significant savings can be made by suiting the size of HIPPOBAGS to your specific needs.','Facilities Management','','inherit','open','open','','14-autosave-v1','','','2015-04-08 09:47:50','2015-04-08 08:47:50','',14,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/14-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(392,2,'2015-03-16 11:08:38','2015-03-16 11:08:38','','installation-hippo','','inherit','open','open','','plasterboard','','','2015-04-08 09:40:24','2015-04-08 08:40:24','',15,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/plasterboard.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(480,2,'2015-04-08 09:54:32','2015-04-08 08:54:32','<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-392\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/plasterboard.jpg\" alt=\"plasterboard HIPPO\" width=\"400\" height=\"553\" />HIPPO Provide Waste Logistics Services for Recycling Plasterboard</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHIPPOWASTE can provide quick and reliable service to allow you to remove excess plasterboard from your site. As part of our commitment to responsible and ethical waste logistics, our dedicated plasterboard disposal and recycling scheme means that we recycle 100% of uncontaminated plasterboard that we collect.\r\n<h2>Segregation</h2>\r\nIn addition to collecting plasterboard, HIPPO\'s reliable, flexible and convenient service allows the segregation of different types of waste from your project. This means that you can easily increase your company’s recycling rates, as well as saving money on landfill tax.\r\n<h2>recycling</h2>\r\nHIPPO recycle around 90 per cent of the waste that we collect, so provide a responsible method of removing waste from your project. We also offer reviews of environmental performance on a site by site basis – including a collection method, a breakdown by waste stream and percentage of landfill diversion.\r\n<h2>national service</h2>\r\nWe offer a national waste logistics service, meaning that both regional and national operations are ideally suited to HIPPO. We can handle your entire waste logistics operation, so there is no need for you to deal with several separate companies for your waste needs.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGS are non-bulky and lightweight, meaning that space can be saved on-site whilst you are undertaking your project. In addition to being an affordable price, strong, convenient HIPPOBAGs come in three different sizes, so you can suit the size of HIPPOBAG used for your specific project and save money.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/case-studies/plasterboard-recycling-case-study/\">Read our Plasterboard Recycling case study here.</a>','Plasterboard Recycling','','inherit','open','open','','15-revision-v1','','','2015-04-08 09:54:32','2015-04-08 08:54:32','',15,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/15-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(393,2,'2015-03-16 11:09:30','2015-03-16 11:09:30','<h2>HIPPO Provide Waste Logistics Services for Recycling Plasterboard</h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/plasterboard.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-392\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/plasterboard.jpg\" alt=\"plasterboard HIPPO\" width=\"300\" height=\"415\" /></a>\r\n\r\nHIPPOWASTE can provide quick and reliable service to allow you to remove excess plasterboard from your site. As part of our commitment to responsible and ethical waste logistics, our dedicated plasterboard disposal and recycling scheme means that we recycle 100% of uncontaminated plasterboard that we collect.\r\n<h2>Segregation</h2>\r\nIn addition to collecting plasterboard, HIPPO\'s reliable, flexible and convenient service allows the segregation of different types of waste from your project. This means that you can easily increase your company’s recycling rates, as well as saving money on landfill tax.\r\n<h2>recycling</h2>\r\nHIPPO recycle around 90 per cent of the waste that we collect, so provide a responsible method of removing waste from your project. We also offer reviews of environmental performance on a site by site basis – including a collection method, a breakdown by waste stream and percentage of landfill diversion.\r\n<h2>national service</h2>\r\nWe offer a national waste logistics service, meaning that both regional and national operations are ideally suited to HIPPO. We can handle your entire waste logistics operation, so there is no need for you to deal with several separate companies for your waste needs.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGS are non-bulky and lightweight, meaning that space can be saved on-site whilst you are undertaking your project. In addition to being an affordable price, strong, convenient HIPPOBAGs come in three different sizes, so you can suit the size of HIPPOBAG used for your specific project and save money.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/case-studies/plasterboard-recycling-case-study/\">Read our Plasterboard Recycling case study here.</a>','Plasterboard Recycling','','inherit','open','open','','15-revision-v1','','','2015-03-16 11:09:30','2015-03-16 11:09:30','',15,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/15-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(394,2,'2015-03-16 11:09:53','2015-03-16 11:09:53','<h2>HIPPO Provide Waste Logistics Services for Recycling Plasterboard</h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/plasterboard.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-392\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/plasterboard.jpg\" alt=\"plasterboard HIPPO\" width=\"400\" height=\"553\" /></a>\r\n\r\nHIPPOWASTE can provide quick and reliable service to allow you to remove excess plasterboard from your site. As part of our commitment to responsible and ethical waste logistics, our dedicated plasterboard disposal and recycling scheme means that we recycle 100% of uncontaminated plasterboard that we collect.\r\n<h2>Segregation</h2>\r\nIn addition to collecting plasterboard, HIPPO\'s reliable, flexible and convenient service allows the segregation of different types of waste from your project. This means that you can easily increase your company’s recycling rates, as well as saving money on landfill tax.\r\n<h2>recycling</h2>\r\nHIPPO recycle around 90 per cent of the waste that we collect, so provide a responsible method of removing waste from your project. We also offer reviews of environmental performance on a site by site basis – including a collection method, a breakdown by waste stream and percentage of landfill diversion.\r\n<h2>national service</h2>\r\nWe offer a national waste logistics service, meaning that both regional and national operations are ideally suited to HIPPO. We can handle your entire waste logistics operation, so there is no need for you to deal with several separate companies for your waste needs.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGS are non-bulky and lightweight, meaning that space can be saved on-site whilst you are undertaking your project. In addition to being an affordable price, strong, convenient HIPPOBAGs come in three different sizes, so you can suit the size of HIPPOBAG used for your specific project and save money.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/case-studies/plasterboard-recycling-case-study/\">Read our Plasterboard Recycling case study here.</a>','Plasterboard Recycling','','inherit','open','open','','15-revision-v1','','','2015-03-16 11:09:53','2015-03-16 11:09:53','',15,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/15-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(395,2,'2015-03-16 11:15:15','2015-03-16 11:15:15','','galliford-try-plasterboard','','inherit','open','open','','galliford-try-plasterboard','','','2015-03-16 11:15:30','2015-03-16 11:15:30','',30,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/galliford-try-plasterboard.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(477,2,'2015-04-08 09:47:57','2015-04-08 08:47:57','<h2><a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-476\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities.jpg\" alt=\"facilities HIPPO\" width=\"400\" height=\"594\" /></a>HIPPO Provide Waste Logistics for Facilities Management</h2>\r\nUsing the HIPPOBAG for the segregation of heavy or substantial inert waste streams, or for any unscheduled or ad hoc waste removal needs will benefit your business in a number of ways.\r\n\r\nHIPPO offer a professional, reliable and fully national service, meaning that we can manage your waste logistics needs across your entire regional or national store estate. HIPPOWASTE can work alongside any existing contracts that your business has in place, delivering an efficient reconstructed waste logistics operation, should you require more than your current contracts are able to deliver.\r\n<h2>flexible</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE offer a flexible and convenient service that can work around your needs; there are no restricting time limits when using our services and you can arrange a pick up at a suitable time for you.\r\n<h2>reputation</h2>\r\nOur reputation for facilities management services has meant that thousands of HIPPOBAGs are collected from store estates weekly. We ensure that waste we collect is disposed of in an ethical manner, with over 90 per cent of the waste that we collect being recycled.\r\n<h2>3 different sizes</h2>\r\nHIPPOBAGs come in three separate sizes and are non-bulky and affordable. Buying the right sized bag for your waste logistics needs will mean that your business will save money, as well as valuable space on site. When used throughout a business on a national or regional store level, significant savings can be made by suiting the size of HIPPOBAGS to your specific needs.','Facilities Management','','inherit','open','open','','14-revision-v1','','','2015-04-08 09:47:57','2015-04-08 08:47:57','',14,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/14-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(402,2,'2015-03-16 11:35:36','2015-03-16 11:35:36','<h2>HIPPO Provide Waste Logistics for Facilities Management</h2>\r\nUsing the HIPPOBAG for the segregation of heavy or substantial inert waste streams, or for any unscheduled or ad hoc waste removal needs will benefit your business in a number of ways.\r\n\r\nHIPPO offer a professional, reliable and fully national service, meaning that we can manage your waste logistics needs across your entire regional or national store estate. HIPPOWASTE can work alongside any existing contracts that your business has in place, delivering an efficient reconstructed waste logistics operation, should you require more than your current contracts are able to deliver.\r\n<h2>flexible</h2>\r\nHIPPOWASTE offer a flexible and convenient service that can work around your needs; there are no restricting time limits when using our services and you can arrange a pick up at a suitable time for you.\r\n<h2>reputation</h2>\r\nOur reputation for facilities management services has meant that thousands of HIPPOBAGs are collected from store estates weekly. We ensure that waste we collect is disposed of in an ethical manner, with over 90 per cent of the waste that we collect being recycled.\r\n<h2>3 different sizes</h2>\r\nHIPPOBAGs come in three separate sizes and are non-bulky and affordable. Buying the right sized bag for your waste logistics needs will mean that your business will save money, as well as valuable space on site. When used throughout a business on a national or regional store level, significant savings can be made by suiting the size of HIPPOBAGS to your specific needs.<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities-management1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-391 size-full\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facilities-management1.jpg\" alt=\"facilities-management\" width=\"1215\" height=\"537\" /></a>','Facilities Management','','inherit','open','open','','14-revision-v1','','','2015-03-16 11:35:36','2015-03-16 11:35:36','',14,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/14-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(397,2,'2015-03-16 11:17:10','2015-03-16 11:17:10','<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/galliford-try-plasterboard.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-395\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/galliford-try-plasterboard.jpg\" alt=\"Galliford Try Plasterboard HIPPO\" width=\"331\" height=\"500\" /></a>Galliford Try used the HIPPOBAG system for disposing of the waste generated from a major refurbishment project of a building that was being converted into student accommodation. This meant creating a lot of small rooms using plasterboard.\r\n\r\nWith the aid of pallet trucks, Galliford Try were able to manoeuvre HIPPOBAGs within confined spaces to position them close to where work was being carried out. Once full, the timely collection guarded against double-handling of waste and the subsequent downtime usually associated with waiting for a skip to be delivered and collected.\r\n\r\nFurthermore, plasterboard was recently reclassified as a non-inert waste that now needs to be disposed of separately at landfill at an increased cost. Different to traditional containers for waste, the HIPPOBAGs made it easier for the team on site to segregate the plasterboard from other waste materials so that it could be recycled, rather than sent to landfill.\r\n<h3>What they Said About HIPPOWASTE</h3>\r\n<em>\"The HIPPOBAG has not only provided Galliford Try with enhanced operational efficiences on site but also the ultimate solution for the segregation and subsequent recycling of plasterboard.\"</em>\r\n\r\nTerry O\'Neil, Site Manager, Galliford Try','Plasterboard Recycling with Galliford Try','','inherit','open','open','','30-revision-v1','','','2015-03-16 11:17:10','2015-03-16 11:17:10','',30,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/30-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(398,2,'2015-03-16 11:25:15','2015-03-16 11:25:15','','constuction-casestudy','','inherit','open','open','','retail-casestudy','','','2015-04-08 09:53:27','2015-04-08 08:53:27','',31,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-casestudy.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(409,1,'2015-03-23 06:31:37','2015-03-23 06:31:37','<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-casestudy-e1426505179570.jpg\"><img class=\"  alignright wp-image-398\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-casestudy-e1426505179570.jpg\" alt=\"Retail casestudy HIPPO\" width=\"369\" height=\"550\" /></a>Where working space is often at a premium, the HIPPOBAG provides an efficient and environmentally sound method of waste segregation and disposal. McLaren Construction recently used the HIPPOBAG to boost environmental performance whilst undertaking their first joint construction and fit-out of a John Lewis Partnership At Home store.\r\n\r\nHIPPOWASTE recommended using the MIDIBAG as the most flexible solution; the one cubic yard bags fit comfortably on a standard pallet, allowing easy movement around site using a fork lift or pallet truck. Flat-packed bags were delivered in bulk ready to be placed near the source of the waste, reducing costly double-handling and minimising Health and Safety risks.\r\n\r\nThe bags were then consolidated for regular collection, preventing waste build up on site which could have restricted the project\'s delivery programme. To support the on-site team, HIPPOWASTE delivered Toolbox Talks to promote best practice when it comes to positioning, filling and arranging collection of the bags.\r\n\r\nLocating HIPPOBAGs at the point of waste generation allowed McLaren to keep working areas tidy. By labelling the bags for each major waste stream, McLaren were able to fully segregate their material. This proactive approach meant HIPPOWASTE have reported that 97% of the waste collected was diverted from landfill and recycled.\r\n\r\n[quote]\r\n<h3>What They Said About HIPPOWASTE</h3>\r\n<em>\"Working in partnership with HIPPOWASTE on this project was the ideal solution. The MIDIBAGS allowed us to keep the site tidy, whilst segregating the waste before collection boosted our recycling rates resulting in 97% diversion from landfill.\"</em>\r\n\r\nLeigh Steele, Fit-out Manager, McLaren Construction\r\n\r\n[/quote]','Interior Fit-Out with John Lewis and McLaren Construction','','inherit','open','open','','31-revision-v1','','','2015-03-23 06:31:37','2015-03-23 06:31:37','',31,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/31-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(399,2,'2015-03-16 11:27:14','2015-03-16 11:27:14','<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-casestudy-e1426505179570.jpg\"><img class=\"  alignright wp-image-398\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/retail-casestudy-e1426505179570.jpg\" alt=\"Retail casestudy HIPPO\" width=\"369\" height=\"550\" /></a>Where working space is often at a premium, the HIPPOBAG provides an efficient and environmentally sound method of waste segregation and disposal. McLaren Construction recently used the HIPPOBAG to boost environmental performance whilst undertaking their first joint construction and fit-out of a John Lewis Partnership At Home store.\r\n\r\nHIPPOWASTE recommended using the MIDIBAG as the most flexible solution; the one cubic yard bags fit comfortably on a standard pallet, allowing easy movement around site using a fork lift or pallet truck. Flat-packed bags were delivered in bulk ready to be placed near the source of the waste, reducing costly double-handling and minimising Health and Safety risks.\r\n\r\nThe bags were then consolidated for regular collection, preventing waste build up on site which could have restricted the project\'s delivery programme. To support the on-site team, HIPPOWASTE delivered Toolbox Talks to promote best practice when it comes to positioning, filling and arranging collection of the bags.\r\n\r\nLocating HIPPOBAGs at the point of waste generation allowed McLaren to keep working areas tidy. By labelling the bags for each major waste stream, McLaren were able to fully segregate their material. This proactive approach meant HIPPOWASTE have reported that 97% of the waste collected was diverted from landfill and recycled.\r\n<h3>What They Said About HIPPOWASTE</h3>\r\n<em>\"Working in partnership with HIPPOWASTE on this project was the ideal solution. The MIDIBAGS allowed us to keep the site tidy, whilst segregating the waste before collection boosted our recycling rates resulting in 97% diversion from landfill.\"</em>\r\n\r\nLeigh Steele, Fit-out Manager, McLaren Construction','Interior Fit-Out with John Lewis and McLaren Construction','','inherit','open','open','','31-revision-v1','','','2015-03-16 11:27:14','2015-03-16 11:27:14','',31,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/31-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(400,2,'2015-03-16 11:31:14','2015-03-16 11:31:14','','Interior-HIPPO','','inherit','open','open','','contruction-casestudy','','','2015-04-08 09:52:36','2015-04-08 08:52:36','',32,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/contruction-casestudy.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(401,2,'2015-03-16 11:32:09','2015-03-16 11:32:09','<img class=\"alignright wp-image-400\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/contruction-casestudy.jpg\" alt=\"Construction Casestudy HIPPO\" width=\"368\" height=\"550\" />HIPPOWASTE was awarded the waste management contract by Wates Retail for the construction of Europe’s largest John Lewis department store in Liverpool. The new 240,000 square foot, multi-million pound John Lewis store is part of The Paradise Project – a regeneration project covering 42 acres in the heart of the city.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAt over five storeys high, this complex construction development required a flexible, easily transportable waste removal solution. Using HIPPOBAGs enabled Wates to set up waste segregation on each of the four sales floors, making it easy for the site teams to separate the waste at source.\r\n\r\nThe bags could then be easily manoeuvred to the ground floor, where they were placed for collection with no need to double handle the waste into another container.\r\n<h3>What they Said About HIPPOWASTE</h3>\r\n<em>\"The different sized HIPPOBAGs are ideal for the various waste streams generated on site and to date the flexibility and versatility afforded by this solution has enabled us to achieve 97% recycling in our first month on site. The friendly and efficient service from HIPPO complements and supports the effort inputted by the site team.\" </em>\r\n\r\nAndy Cartwright, Site Manager, Wates Retail','Construction with Wates Retail and John Lewis','','inherit','open','open','','32-revision-v1','','','2015-03-16 11:32:09','2015-03-16 11:32:09','',32,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/32-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(404,2,'2015-03-16 11:37:29','2015-03-16 11:37:29','<img class=\"alignright wp-image-321\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/careers1.jpg\" alt=\"careers\" width=\"440\" height=\"397\" />The chances are, when you join us, you\'ve got more than a job in mind. You’ll be thinking about how joining HIPPO will contribute to your longer term aims – and so will we.\r\n<h2>opportunities</h2>\r\nWe work to provide opportunities for development through both training and through career development. Our training is themed around individuals’ career objectives, departmental requirements, and wider business needs or changes, making sure we’re all ready for our next challenge.\r\n<h2>progression</h2>\r\nWe are particularly proud of our team’s career progression – we’re not a huge organisation, but through creative thinking, an eye for talent, and the flexibility that comes with the Company’s growth and development, we have been able to spot opportunities for people to move to roles which are more senior, more challenging, or represent a change of career. This is great for us, as we retain our committed and talented people; and it allows people with talent and ambition to pursue their career aspirations. 9% of our team were promoted into their current roles, and 12% have moved to a different role during their time with HIPPO.\r\n<h2>how to apply</h2>\r\nTo apply for any of vacancies, please email your CV with a covering letter to recruitment@hippowaste.co.uk or post it to: HR Department, HIPPO, 1000 Lakeside, North Harbour, Portsmouth PO6 3EN\r\n<h2>Current Vacancies</h2>\r\nWe have no current vacancies.','Careers at HIPPOWASTE','','inherit','open','open','','34-revision-v1','','','2015-03-16 11:37:29','2015-03-16 11:37:29','',34,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/34-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(446,0,'2015-04-01 12:43:08','2015-04-01 11:43:08','','Daily backup - April 1, 2015','','publish','open','open','','daily-backup-april-1-2015','','','2015-04-01 12:43:08','2015-04-01 11:43:08','',0,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/daily-backup-april-1-2015/',0,'revisr_commits','',0),(412,1,'2015-03-23 06:32:58','2015-03-23 06:32:58','<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">HIPPO is a national provider of flexible, convenient and ethical waste solutions and the operations behind the HIPPOBAG</h1>','Home','','inherit','open','open','','17-revision-v1','','','2015-03-23 06:32:58','2015-03-23 06:32:58','',17,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/17-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(413,1,'2015-03-23 06:33:42','2015-03-23 06:33:42','<h2>MIDIBAG</h2>\r\n<img class=\" size-medium wp-image-321 alignleft\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/careers1-300x271.jpg\" alt=\"careers\" width=\"300\" height=\"271\" />\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<strong>1 cubic yard</strong>\r\n<strong> 1 tonne</strong>\r\nThe MIDIBAG was the first HIPPOBAG, and is still the most popular product we offer for home DIY and gardening projects.\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>MEGABAG</h2>\r\n<img class=\" size-full wp-image-575 alignleft\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Mega.jpg\" alt=\"Mega\" width=\"500\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<strong>1.5 cubic yards</strong>\r\n<strong> 1.5 tonnes</strong>\r\n\r\nPerfect for disposing of your old bathroom suite (that\'s what we designed it for) as well as general garden, household and DIY waste.\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>MIGHTYBAG</h2>\r\n<strong><img class=\" size-full wp-image-576 alignleft\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Mighty.jpg\" alt=\"Mighty\" width=\"650\" height=\"400\" /></strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>4.5 cubic yards</strong>\r\n<strong>1.5 tonnes</strong>\r\n\r\nIdeal for disposing of your kitchen or bathroom rip out, general garden, DIY or household waste. Due to it’s large size, the MIGHTYBAG can only be filled up to 1/4 full with heavy waste such as soil/bricks.','Our Products','','publish','open','open','','our-products','','','2015-06-05 16:30:56','2015-06-05 15:30:56','',8,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?page_id=413',0,'page','',0),(414,1,'2015-03-23 06:33:42','2015-03-23 06:33:42','','Our Products','','inherit','open','open','','413-revision-v1','','','2015-03-23 06:33:42','2015-03-23 06:33:42','',413,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/413-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(415,1,'2015-03-23 06:36:24','2015-03-23 06:36:24',' ','','','publish','open','open','','415','','','2015-05-20 11:21:46','2015-05-20 10:21:46','',8,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=415',16,'nav_menu_item','',0),(417,1,'2015-03-23 06:37:06','2015-03-23 06:37:06','','Companies We Work With','','inherit','open','open','','416-revision-v1','','','2015-03-23 06:37:06','2015-03-23 06:37:06','',416,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/416-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(418,1,'2015-03-23 06:37:46','2015-03-23 06:37:46',' ','','','publish','open','open','','418','','','2015-05-20 11:21:46','2015-05-20 10:21:46','',7,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=418',13,'nav_menu_item','',0),(419,1,'2015-03-23 07:05:19','2015-03-23 07:05:19','','Added plugin','','publish','closed','closed','','added-plugin','','','2015-03-23 07:05:19','2015-03-23 07:05:19','',0,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?post_type=revisr_commits&#038;p=419',0,'revisr_commits','',0),(445,0,'2015-03-31 08:45:02','2015-03-31 07:45:02','','Daily backup - March 31, 2015','','publish','open','open','','daily-backup-march-31-2015','','','2015-03-31 08:45:02','2015-03-31 07:45:02','',0,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/daily-backup-march-31-2015/',0