'publish','open','open','','daily-backup-may-18-2015','','','2015-05-18 21:07:23','2015-05-18 20:07:23','',0,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/daily-backup-may-18-2015/',0,'revisr_commits','',0),(505,0,'2015-05-20 07:07:42','2015-05-20 06:07:42','','Daily backup - May 20, 2015','','publish','open','open','','daily-backup-may-20-2015','','','2015-05-20 07:07:42','2015-05-20 06:07:42','',0,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/daily-backup-may-20-2015/',0,'revisr_commits','',0),(521,0,'2015-06-01 10:58:12','2015-06-01 09:58:12','','Daily backup - June 1, 2015','','publish','open','open','','daily-backup-june-1-2015','','','2015-06-01 10:58:12','2015-06-01 09:58:12','',0,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/daily-backup-june-1-2015/',0,'revisr_commits','',0),(508,0,'2015-05-20 08:49:09','2015-05-20 07:49:09','','Daily backup - May 20, 2015','','publish','open','open','','daily-backup-may-20-2015-2','','','2015-05-20 08:49:09','2015-05-20 07:49:09','',0,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/daily-backup-may-20-2015-2/',0,'revisr_commits','',0),(510,2,'2015-05-20 11:13:04','2015-05-20 10:13:04','<h2>HIPPO Provide Waste Logistics Services to Projects Across the Construction Sector</h2>\r\nFrom helping you plan the volume and types of waste you’ll encounter, to knowing where your waste is going and what level of recycling you can achieve, HIPPO works with you from start to finish to help to deliver your project efficiently. What’s more, our national transport infrastructure means wherever you are, you will receive a reliable collection service that you can trust.\r\n<h2>Flexible</h2>\r\nThe flexibility of HIPPOBAGs allow for easy waste collection from tight, restricted sites. In addition, our national service means we can offer you a solution wherever you are in the country.\r\n\r\nConstruction sites nationwide use HIPPO because of the convenience and reliability of our lightweight and flexible HIPPOBAGs, as well as our excellent customer service. Collections can be made from different areas on large sites, including from scaffolding or loading bays, helping you to improve site efficiency.\r\n<h2>Ethical</h2>\r\nHIPPO can also ensure that you only have one supplier for all of your site waste needs, including hazardous waste and <a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/services/plasterboard-recycling/\">plasterboard</a>. We recycle around 90 per cent of the waste that we collect, so you can rest assured that your operation will be carried out ethically and responsibly.\r\n<h2>Bespoke</h2>\r\nDifferent bag sizes make it easy to segregate waste streams and achieve diversion from landfill objectives, whilst a variety of size options mean that you only ever pay for what you need, as well as saving space on site. HIPPO offer bespoke solutions developed for each site, giving you flexibility in collection volumes, as well as in the time or date of collection.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/case-studies/construction-case-study/\">Read our Construction case study here</a>.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction22.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-452\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/construction22.jpg\" alt=\"construction HIPPO\" width=\"1015\" height=\"489\" /></a>','Construction','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2015-05-20 11:13:04','2015-05-20 10:13:04','',10,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(512,2,'2015-05-20 11:20:17','2015-05-20 10:20:17','<img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-563\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/HIPPO-POS.png\" alt=\"HIPPO POS\" width=\"264\" height=\"563\" />Our HIPPOBAG range is available nationally to both the public and trade professionals, in DIY stores, garden centres and independent retailers. With a presence in over 2,000 stores across the UK, HIPPOBAGs are never far away.\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGs are sold on high impact point of sale displays. With a variety of solutions available, HIPPOBAGs can be adapted to any store environment whether it’s one store or a thousand!\r\n\r\nHIPPOBAGs offer the perfect flat-packed alternative to skip hire – at a lower cost than a traditional skip. HIPPO is the only UK waste management specialist with the infrastructure to offer a nationwide bag collection service. A hassle free product and service that your customer will love!\r\n\r\nTo find out how you can become a stockist, or for more information about HIPPOBAGs, give us a call on 0345 850 0850.\r\n<h2>Currently Stocked In:</h2>\r\n<img class=\" size-full wp-image-566 alignleft\" src=\"http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Retail-Logos.jpg\" alt=\"Retail Logos\" width=\"760\" height=\"60\" />','Retailers','','publish','open','open','','retailers','','','2015-06-05 15:49:22','2015-06-05 14:49:22','',0,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?page_id=512',0,'page','',0),(513,2,'2015-05-20 11:20:17','2015-05-20 10:20:17','Text to be supplied','Retailers','','inherit','open','open','','512-revision-v1','','','2015-05-20 11:20:17','2015-05-20 10:20:17','',512,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/512-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(514,2,'2015-05-20 11:21:46','2015-05-20 10:21:46',' ','','','publish','open','open','','514','','','2015-05-20 11:21:46','2015-05-20 10:21:46','',0,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/?p=514',8,'nav_menu_item','',0),(515,2,'2015-05-20 11:23:49','2015-05-20 10:23:49','Content to be supplied','Retailers','','inherit','open','open','','512-revision-v1','','','2015-05-20 11:23:49','2015-05-20 10:23:49','',512,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/512-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(516,0,'2015-05-21 09:42:06','2015-05-21 08:42:06','','Daily backup - May 21, 2015','','publish','open','open','','daily-backup-may-21-2015','','','2015-05-21 09:42:06','2015-05-21 08:42:06','',0,'http://hippo.tailoreddev.co.uk/blog/daily-backup-may-21-2015/',0,'revisr_commit